data.text:
MUMBAI: It’s time for the latest and upcoming spoilers in your favourite shows. Read on!

Kabeer and Zara escape from Miraj’s clutches in Zee TV’s Ishq Subhan Allah

Kabeer and Zara manage to escape from Miraj’s trap, and Zara now wants to find out the girl who was buried instead of her and her parents. Kabeer realizes that Miraj had swapped the girl, and to find out more about her, they head to the police station. There, they meet the girl’s father and take him to the place of burial.

Pancham gets beaten up in SAB TV’s Jijaji Chhat Par Hain

Pintu calls off his friendship with Pancham and calls him selfish. He feels Pancham has taken advantage of his friendship. Meanwhile, Karuna disguises herself and teams up with Murari to beat Pancham up.

Manjari to confess her wrongdoings in &TV’s Siddhivinayak?

All the preparations are on for the maha aarti of Ganeshji. Prachi is clicking a selfie wearing a gold necklace. She tells Rajbir that she has earned it from Manjari. Everyone is ready for the aarti. Vin gives the aarti to Rudra. Rudra holds Siddhi's hand and performs the aarti with her. The Pandit asks to get the har. While Siddhi requests Manjari to get the har from her room, she sneaks up and calls Gauri. Gauri is waiting in Manjari's room dressed as Vaibhavi. Will Manjari finally confess to her wrongdoings?

(Also Read: Karan SACRIFICES Preeta for Rishab in Kundali Bhagya, Kiara IN DANGER in Kumkum Bhagya, and other Spoiler Updates)

Arjun refuses to listen to Krishna in &TV’s Paramavatar Shree Krishna

Krishna, Sudama, and Balram have reached the ashram of Sandivni, and the Sandivni accepts Sudama as his pupil and honours Krishna also as his pupil. Arjun encounters a wild boar on a cliff and has no place to run. Krishna tells Arjun to kill the boar but Arjun refuses.
